altername_name: Medarot 5: The Transfer Student of Susutake Village - Kabuto Version
name: Medarot 5: Susutake Mura no Tenkousei Kabuto Version
overview: The final Medarot/Medabots game on the Game Boy Color and the last canon RPG game until Medarot DS nearly a decade later. It features a new protagonist, Koishimaru Tensan, who has recently moved to the small town of Susutake.
